imple plan of &quot;We barsh dems guud n dems go splat, HAR HAR!&quot;  Me likes ta barsh dat way.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   But den da monsters am gits tuffer n dems no fall down so eezee.  <br><br>Now we am have ta buff up so we can barsh dems guud.  We make shure da healers gots da mojo fer da heelin.  We make sure da 'channer am gots da mojo n da levels fer da mezzin.  We gits da druid n da ranjer ta do da harmony.  Maybe we am keep da spawn broken so we am no gets more den we am ta handles.  We makes shure dems snared n engulfed or reddee ta root dems so dems no run off n cause us ta agro nudderwun before we am reddee.  <br><br>We also makes shure dat we am know whut jobs peepuls gots in da groop.  If'n yuse join groop yuse ask &quot;whut am yuse wunt me ta do?&quot; if'n yuse am no know.  Maybe dems just wunt yuse ta heal.  Maybe yuse da puller.  Maybe yuse tank da adds dt no can mezz.  Maybe yuse do da buffin.  Maybe dems got bunches jobs fer yuse.<br><br>N yuse need ta tink bowt crowd contol.  Many times yuse am goin in ta dungeon ta kill da badies.  It am dere home turf.  Dems more den yuse.  Yuse no own da zone, but yuse can control its.  Yuse find guud pull to points.  Yuse learn where da mobs pops.  If'n yuse find owts, yuse time da pops so yuse know when dem ready fer poppin so dems no gits da jump on yuse n yuse no pull extra when dems comin.<br>Crowd control am not just da job of da channer.  Dems makes it easier but evereewun am gonna do dis stuff.  <br><br>Lots of peepul am gots root.  Yuse may need ta have dat up so yuse can root da badies away frum da uther peepuls.  Roots will break if'n yuse nuke or barsh tuu hard, so if'n it am rooted yuse no barsh.  Yuse also duz bestest to stay away frum da rooted badies cuz dem still fightin.<br><br>Da mezz.  Peepul likes da channers cuz dems gots breezee in da head fer da mojo n dems gots da attackin' speed spells n dems gots da mezz.  But here am tings dat yuse am need ta know bowt mezz.  <br>1. If'n sumthin mezzed, yuse not hits it.  It take damage, it am break da mezz.  it den go barsh da channer or healers.  If yuse am mezzin, no Area effect procs or spells.  Dems break da mezz.<br>2.  If'n it am DOTed, den it am no can be mezzed.<br>3.  Yuse can back up da mezzes wit roots n' snares.  No engulfin darkness (dat am DOT).  Yuse can also duz much debuffin like da slow spells n utherwuns dat no break da mezz.  Dat way when we am ready ta barsh da mezzed wun den we am can fites.<br>4.  Watch fer da hotkey messages fer mezzin.  Sumtimes tings happen reel fast n da channer am just mezzin da stuff den hims pick new target.  It am possible dat yuse need ta reassist so yuse on da right target.<br>5.  Dis am portant wun; Enchanters need to be of a high enough level so tings are blue so dems guud fer mezzin.  When channers try ta mezz da reds n yellows, dems wastin mana.  So if'n yuse need channer fer mezzin makes sure dems no bitin off more den dems can chew.<br>6.  Pets.  If'n yuse gots pet, yuse take yer time before yuse assist wit barshin.  If yer pet am attackin da one dat need mezzin, den yuse can say &quot;buh-bye&quot; ta Jobobaner or Goner cuz hims am goner.<br>7.  Taunt.  It am guud ider ta taunt 3 times before breakin da mezz.  Dat way if yuse duz dat den da baddies am tinks da tank wit da armir n' da hitpoints am most portant ting ta hit instead of da healers or da channer.  Dems build up agro guud.<br><br>Pullin am nuther portant part.  If'n yuse da puller, yuse sets da pace fer da barshin.  But yuse am no just go nuts n sez we barsh em all n hopes dat yer healers n casters am pull da mojo frum dems butt.  Dems onlee gots whut dems gots.  here am uther tings dat am portant.<br><br>1.  Learn how ta pull an area.  If'n yuse am new n yuse am need ta learn where ta pull frum cuz yuse am gonna be dere again, learn frum palz yuse barshin wit.<br>2.  Learn ta break up da spawn.  Wunce yuse duz da break in n sum places, yuse can pull dems solo cuz dems no poppin tagedders no more.<br>3.  Werk wit da Mezzers n harmonizers n Soothers n rooters.  If yuse need sumwun ta do sumthin ta help wit da pullin send dems in.<br>4.  Learn da agro ranges.  Sumtimes da monsters am far enough apart dat yuse can pull one wit out agroin da uthers.  Sometimes dems wander to close to da uthers n yuse no can pulls dems wit' out dems bringin palz.<br>5.  Move da group if yuse need to.  Sumtimes yuse am werkin yer way into da dungeon or maybe yuse find named spawn fer da barshin.  Yuse move da groop ta go barsh.<br>6.  Just cuz sumwun am monk no mean dems guud puller.  Me know bunches guud monk pullers dat use da feign death so dems no agro too much.  Me also seen bunches dat am no got no buziness pullin cuz dems am dummeez.  Yuse watch fer dat n makes shure yuse no agro palz when yuse do da feign death.<br>7.  Peelin'.  If yuse am werkin wit a Monk dat am Feign deathin, den yuse can peel.  Dis am guud tactic.  It am whut yuse need fer Plane raids.  Dis am how its goes.  Monk pulls bunches mobs.  Hims gits close to da groop (not to close).  Hims falls down n plays dead.  Monsters am git kornfuzed n' no hits da monk.  Dems start ta wonder off.  If'n lucky dems take off one at a time.  Den when just a couple left, da peeler goes 'thwip' wit da arrows n pulls da baddies <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   den we am call owts da assists n da enchanters duz da mezzin on da extra dat come.  Dis am guud barshin.<br>8.  Pathing.  Sum baddies have dere own ider bowt how dems go go ta yuse.  Dems no takes da short cuts sum times.  Sometimes dems run into palz n grabs dem fer da barshin.  Watch fer dis.  It can make da difference between a single pull n' da whole dungeon barshin yuse.<br>9. Chain pullin.  Dis can be tricky.  Dis am da ider.  Yuse pull one or 2 baddies.  Mezz/root one den start barshin da uther wun.  Den when hims dead yuse barsh da uther one dat am waitin' an den da puller go n gits more fer barshin n' when it am der yuse mezz/root da new wun n da puller helps finish barshin da last wun.  It can gits kornfuin so yuse becareful n makeshure yer groop know whut yuse doin.<br><br>Okies me add more laterz.  Me gots ta go do sum barshin.  Wun last ting.  If'n yuse got plan n stick to da plan n sumwun die, den it am just minor setback.  It am happens /shrug.  If sumwun gits Kornfuzed n duz sumthin dat am gets peepul keeled, make shure yuse learn frum its so yuse no have dat happens again.  Maybe yuse just need ta iron owt da kommunikashun (communication). <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  Some times you have to break character to make sure that everyone knows what you are saying.</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END-->  But yuse duz whut yuse need tu fer da barshin so yuse no duz da bad ting again.  But if'n peepul die cuz dems no stick to da plan n dems no learn frum da mistakes dat am when Phread am gits real MAD n dat also when peepul start gittin kicked out of da groop. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START >: --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/mad.gif ALT=">:"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>But me am no likes ta be mad.  Dat am no fun.  Me tink barshin am bestest when yuse n' palz am werkin like team n barshin tagedders <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br> <p><img src=http://wsphotofews.excite.com/005/zf/A6/kp/7w19958.jpg><BR><a href=http://pub63.ezboard.com/bphreadsboard>Phread's Board</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub20.ezboard.com/uladiefalcon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ladiefalcon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 8<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/14/01 12:11:29 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Phread's Barshin Fill-aw-su-fee</span><hr size=1> Thanks for the post... great words of wisdom... If you follow these ideas there will be less deaths and more exp this way..<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I always listen to Phread , He has saved my sweet... little self many many times... thanks Phread..<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Darkfalcon<br>Nytefalcon<br>Ladiefalcon finally 34 and superior Healing... soon exp rez's..<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ))<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub20.ezboard.com/ujendaani.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jendaani</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/globalBlack.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/14/01 6:35:55 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Phread's Barshin Fill-aw-su-fee</span><hr size=1> Phread,<br><br>You are very wise. I am someone who likes to know what the group leader wants me to do.  With only so many spell slots, it helps to know what I should be using!<br><br>Jen <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3F3F3F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub20.ezboard.com/ubjarkibearskin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bjarki Bearskin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 54<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(5/15/01